  "title": "System Application Engineer (X-Ray)",
  "description": "<p>• Design, develop, and enhance X-ray scanning systems, including prototyping and testing of new concepts.</p><p>• Prepare clear manufacturing, assembly, and testing procedures for equipment.</p><p>• Carry out installation, maintenance, and repair works on-site, and conduct customer training when required.</p><p>• Train manufacturing staff on product assembly and testing processes.</p><p>• Support the integration of software with electrical and control systems.</p><p>• Maintain well-structured technical documentation and propose design improvements based on analysis.</p><p>• Assemble, test, and troubleshoot products, providing practical feedback to improve design and performance.</p><p>• Analyze field performance data and recommend product modifications or enhancements.</p><p>• Travel internationally for system evaluations, custom installations, and training assignments.</p><p>• Undertake additional duties as assigned.<br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p></p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
